{"title":"Hellfire (dNetHack)","url":"https://nethackwiki.com/wiki/Hellfire_(dNetHack)","type":"markdown","data":"| )   Hellfire   *(No tile)*            |                                                                                                         |\n| ------------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |\n| Base item                             | [crossbow](/wiki/Crossbow \"Crossbow\")                                                                   |\n|                                       |                                                                                                         |\n| Damage vs. small                      | 1d2 **+1** (+6d6)                                                                                       |\n| Damage vs. large                      | 1d2 **+1** (+6d6)                                                                                       |\n| To-hit bonus                          | **+1d4**                                                                                                |\n| Bonus versus                          | *(any)*                                                                                                 |\n|                                       |                                                                                                         |\n| Weapon skill                          | [crossbow](/wiki/Crossbow \"Crossbow\")                                                                   |\n| Size                                  | one-handed                                                                                              |\n| Affiliation                           | - [chaotic](/wiki/Chaotic \"Chaotic\")                                                                    |\n|                                       |                                                                                                         |\n| When carried                          | *(none)*                                                                                                |\n| When wielded                          | * [fire resistance](/wiki/Fire_resistance \"Fire resistance\")\n* fired bolts cause fiery explosion on hit |\n| When [invoked](/wiki/Invoke \"Invoke\") | *(none)*                                                                                                |\n|                                       |                                                                                                         |\n| Base price                            | 3000 [zm](/wiki/Zorkmid \"Zorkmid\")                                                                      |\n| Weight                                | [50](/wiki/Weight \"Weight\")                                                                             |\n| Material                              | [wood](/wiki/Wood \"Wood\")                                                                               |\n\n**Hellfire** is an [artifact weapon](/wiki/Artifact_weapon \"Artifact weapon\") that appears in [dNetHack](/wiki/DNetHack \"DNetHack\") and [notdNetHack](/wiki/NotdNetHack \"NotdNetHack\"). It is [chaotic](/wiki/Chaotic \"Chaotic\") for generation purposes, and its [base item](/wiki/Base_item \"Base item\") is a [crossbow](/wiki/Crossbow \"Crossbow\").\n\n## Generation\n\nChaotic characters can receive Hellfire as a [sacrifice gift](/wiki/Sacrifice_gift \"Sacrifice gift\").\n\n## Description\n\nHellfire confers [fire resistance](/wiki/Fire_resistance \"Fire resistance\") while wielded, and bolts fired from it have a +1d4 [to-hit](/wiki/To-hit \"To-hit\") bonus and deal +1 fire damage to monsters without fire resistance - the bolts will additionally cause an explosion of [fire](/wiki/Fire \"Fire\") in a 3x3 radius centered on a monster that it hits, consuming the bolt and dealing 6d6 damage to monsters caught in the explosion.\n\n- *This page is a **[stub](/wiki/Category:Stubs \"Category:Stubs\")**. Should you wish to do so, you can contribute by [**expanding this page**.](https://nethackwiki.com/index.php?title=Hellfire_\\(dNetHack\\)\\&action=edit)*\n\n[![This article describes a 3.4.3-based variant of NetHack. Click here for more information.](/images/5/5d/Nh343var-icon.png)](/wiki/NetHackWiki:Next_version \"This article describes a 3.4.3-based variant of NetHack. Click here for more information.\")\n","html":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html class=\"client-nojs\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\"/>\n<title>Hellfire (dNetHack) - NetHack Wiki</title>\n<script>document.documentElement.className = document.documentElement.className.replace( /(^|\\s)client-nojs(\\s|$)/, \"$1client-js$2\" );</script>\n<script>(window.RLQ=window.RLQ||[]).push(function(){mw.config.set({\"wgCanonicalNamespace\":\"\",\"wgCanonicalSpecialPageName\":false,\"wgNamespaceNumber\":0,\"wgPageName\":\"Hellfire_(dNetHack)\",\"wgTitle\":\"Hellfire (dNetHack)\",\"wgCurRevisionId\":167231,\"wgRevisionId\":167231,\"wgArticleId\":40197,\"wgIsArticle\":true,\"wgIsRedirect\":false,\"wgAction\":\"view\",\"wgUserName\":null,\"wgUserGroups\":[\"*\"],\"wgCategories\":[\"Stubs\",\"Variant-343 articles\",\"DNetHack artifact weapons\",\"NotdNetHack artifact weapons\"],\"wgBreakFrames\":false,\"wgPageContentLanguage\":\"en\",\"wgPageContentModel\":\"wikitext\",\"wgSeparatorTransformTable\":[\"\",\"\"],\"wgDigitTransformTable\":[\"\",\"\"],\"wgDefaultDateFormat\":\"dmy\",\"wgMonthNames\":[\"\",\"January\",\"February\",\"March\",\"April\",\"May\",\"June\",\"July\",\"August\",\"September\",\"October\",\"November\",\"December\"],\"wgMonthNamesShort\":[\"\",\"Jan\",\"Feb\",\"Mar\",\"Apr\",\"May\",\"Jun\",\"Jul\",\"Aug\",\"Sep\",\"Oct\",\"Nov\",\"Dec\"],\"wgRelevantPageName\":\"Hellfire_(dNetHack)\",\"wgRelevantArticleId\":40197,\"wgRequestId\":\"3af5591288176a7dd2cbcd82\",\