d colspan=\"2\">\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Weapon skill\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Crossbow\" title=\"Crossbow\">crossbow</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Size\n</th>\n<td>one-handed\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Affiliation\n</th>\n<td>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Chaotic\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Chaotic\">chaotic</a></li></ul>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\">\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>When carried\n</th>\n<td>\n<p><i>(none)</i>\n</p>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>When wielded\n</th>\n<td>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Fire_resistance\" title=\"Fire resistance\">fire resistance</a></li><li>fired bolts cause fiery explosion on hit</li></ul>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>When <a href=\"/wiki/Invoke\" title=\"Invoke\">invoked</a>\n</th>\n<td>\n<p><i>(none)</i>\n</p>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\">\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Base price\n</th>\n<td>3000 <a href=\"/wiki/Zorkmid\" title=\"Zorkmid\">zm</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Weight\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Weight\" title=\"Weight\">50</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Material\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Wood\" title=\"Wood\">wood</a>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n</div>\n<p><b>Hellfire</b> is an <a href=\"/wiki/Artifact_weapon\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Artifact weapon\">artifact weapon</a> that appears in <a href=\"/wiki/DNetHack\" title=\"DNetHack\">dNetHack</a> and <a href=\"/wiki/NotdNetHack\" title=\"NotdNetHack\">notdNetHack</a>. It is <a href=\"/wiki/Chaotic\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Chaotic\">chaotic</a> for generation purposes, and its <a href=\"/wiki/Base_item\" title=\"Base item\">base item</a> is a <a href=\"/wiki/Crossbow\" title=\"Crossbow\">crossbow</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Generation\">Generation</span></h2>\n<p>Chaotic characters can receive Hellfire as a <a href=\"/wiki/Sacrifice_gift\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Sacrifice gift\">sacrifice gift</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Description\">Description</span></h2>\n<p>Hellfire confers <a href=\"/wiki/Fire_resistance\" title=\"Fire resistance\">fire resistance</a> while wielded, and bolts fired from it have a +1d4 <a href=\"/wiki/To-hit\" title=\"To-hit\">to-hit</a> bonus and deal +1 fire damage to monsters without fire resistance - the bolts will additionally cause an explosion of <a href=\"/wiki/Fire\" title=\"Fire\">fire</a> in a 3x3 radius centered on a monster that it hits, consuming the bolt and dealing 6d6 damage to monsters caught in the explosion.\n</p>\n<div class=\"stub\">\n<dl><dd><i>This page is a <b><a href=\"/wiki/Category:Stubs\" title=\"Category:Stubs\">stub</a></b>. Should you wish to do so, you can contribute by <a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://nethackwiki.com/index.php?title=Hellfire_(dNetHack)&amp;action=edit\"><b>expanding this page</b>.</a></i></dd></dl>\n</div>\n<div style=\"display:none; right:10px; padding-bottom: 17px\" class=\"metadata topicon nopopups\"><div style=\"margin-top: -10px\"><a href=\"/wiki/NetHackWiki:Next_version\" title=\"This article describes a 3.4.3-based variant of NetHack. Click here for more information.\"><img alt=\"This article describes a 3.4.3-based variant of NetHack. Click here for more information.\" src=\"/images/5/5d/Nh343var-icon.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20240926184013\nCache expiry: 604800\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.017 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.024 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 172/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 1043/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 2626/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 517/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 1/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   14.016      1 -total\n 53.16%    7.451      1 Template:Artifact_weapon\n 35.44%    4.968      1 Template:Variant-343\n 26.95%    3.778      1 Template:Version_icon\n 21.86%    3.06