</ul>\n  |whenwielded=<ul><li>[[fire resistance]]</li><li>fired bolts cause fiery explosion on hit</li></ul>\n  |cost=3000\n  |weight=50\n  |material=wood\n}}\n\n'''Hellfire''' is an [[artifact weapon]] that appears in [[dNetHack]] and [[notdNetHack]]. It is [[chaotic]] for generation purposes, and its [[base item]] is a [[crossbow]].\n\n==Generation==\nChaotic characters can receive Hellfire as a [[sacrifice gift]].\n\n==Description==\nHellfire confers [[fire resistance]] while wielded, and bolts fired from it have a +1d4 [[to-hit]] bonus and deal +1 fire damage to monsters without fire resistance - the bolts will additionally cause an explosion of [[fire]] in a 3x3 radius centered on a monster that it hits, consuming the bolt and dealing 6d6 damage to monsters caught in the explosion.\n{{stub}}\n{{variant-343}}\n[[Category:dNetHack artifact weapons]]\n[[Category:notdNetHack artifact weapons]]"}